title: Tensei Cinderella wa Glass no Kutsu wo Hakitakunai
description: An overworked OL (office lady) living under the weight of a “black company” reincarnates as Cinderella... in the classic fairy tale world. But this isn't your typical Cinderella story—she refuses to become a princess! A suspenseful twist unfolds as she does everything she can to avoid the fate of wearing glass slippers and marrying the prince.
author: Nanao Mio
